South Africa Seeks to Cut Power Demand by 5,000 Megawatts, Reuters Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-26T15:18:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/south-africa-seeks-to-cut-power-demand-by-5-000-megawatts-reuters-says.html
South Africa  is in talks with energy
intensive users with a view to reducing power demand by about
5,000 megawatts, Reuters reported, citing Energy MinisterDipuo Peters.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
